# rainbow-text
On the first visit, you can create a message to display to someone else using rainbow text. Copy the generated URI on the page and give it to someone else to open. You can disguise the message URI with bitly. (Link on page if you are creating a message)

New Feature: Add a url param "edit=true" before the message='...' param in the url to edit a message after it has been created !!!


Sample Usage
  # TYT
  http://rainbow-text.herokuapp.com/index.html?font-size=118px&font-family=Fantasy&message=%25F0%259F%2590%25BA%2520%2520%2520TYT%2520%2520%2520%25F0%259F%2590%25BA%250AIs%250AToo%250A%25F0%259F%2590%25BE%2520%2520Strong%2520%2520%25F0%259F%2590%25BE%250A

  Sample editing existing message
  http://rainbow-text.herokuapp.com/index.html?edit=true&font-size=118px&font-family=Fantasy&message=%25F0%259F%2590%25BA%2520%2520%2520TYT%2520%2520%2520%25F0%259F%2590%25BA%250AIs%250AToo%250A%25F0%259F%2590%25BE%2520%2520Strong%2520%2520%25F0%259F%2590%25BE


